05f3c10ff2dcccd86ced633ec78593cd933aa7a53d2c8a0aca6a6e6ed5bf9c20bd87325ac22ec4bf536bfbeb247ae58ddc07cd1b2f6da7004a72f846e35dd3f2  stop-deprecated-functions-from-breaking-compilation.patch"
